function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_PRAVA, CONVO_PRAVA_03)
	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_PRAVA, 1)	
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(ID_PRAVA, ANIM_PRAVA_CAST, 2)

	end

end
